Rule Learning, Theory

The paper belongs to the sub-category of Rule Learning as it discusses the task of discovering interesting regularities in sets of data, which is a key aspect of rule learning. The paper also belongs to the sub-category of Theory as it proposes a generalized definition of the data mining task and discusses its properties and relation to the traditional concept learning problem. The paper does not relate to the other sub-categories of AI mentioned in the question.
